    • Weapon

      public Weapon(int damage, double w, double h, double d, double xOffset, double yOffset, double zOffset, processing.core.PImage p)
      Sets the location, dimensions, and the amount of damage the weapon can do
      Parameters:
      damage - The damage of the weapon
      w - The width of the weapon
      h - The height of the weapon
      d - The depth of the weapon
      xOffset - the x-distance between the player and the Weapon
      yOffset - the y-distance between the player and the Weapon
      zOffset - the z-distance between the player and the Weapon
      p - the PApplet in which the Blaster is drawn
